snippet.title: Loggerhead First Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the first Trailer for Loggerhead. You can wish list this retro 1980's Aussie horror game now on steam.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1762850/Loggerhead/

Loggerhead is a classic Survival Horror Experience featuring a retro stylistic aesthetic, choice of two playable characters, fixed camera angles, tank controls and classic puzzle solving. Fans of the original survival horror classics such as Silent Hill and Resident Evil will feel right at home sweet home. Through exploration you will uncover the dark history of Boggarogga Creek a condemned remote Australian camping ground which offers a diverse range of encounters and locations.
